      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="31128677">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/85636775/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="李清远SYSU" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31128677/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31128677/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/85636775/" class=" " title="李清远SYSU">李清远SYSU</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31128677">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">最近重读罗尔纲先生的《太平天国史》。真切体会到作者对研究对象具有真感情，力证李秀成的自述不过是为了策反曾国藩，就像蜀汉亡国后姜维劝钟会反魏的方法复兴蜀国一样。甚至连蒋老水手和陕北老翁这样的只见诸个别史料的下层人物，都一网无遗。在社会史研究上，信奉唯物史观的史家早已入手了。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-04-04 14:10</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
